absmiddle>  A New Drawing Accessory For The Site: Swords</span><hr size=1> Hi, I'm a writer and I like to draw my characters in my stories and show them off to my friends. This site has given me big tips I can use on my next sketches but the characters in my current story don't use guns. One uses a sword, another a scythe, another a bo staff, and a double-edge, (what Serge uses in Chrono Cross). I can't come up with any good stances or fighting poses that really shows the strength and power being used in an outrageous swordfight and I was hoping someone could help me. This is kinda directed to the webmaster of this site: could you add to your Accessories-Yuronova<br>
